				\begin{document}$$max_{PSTH}$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M42"><mml:mrow><mml:mi>m</mml:mi><mml:mi>a</mml:mi><mml:msub><mml:mi>x</mml:mi><mml:mrow><mml:mi mathvariant="italic">PSTH</mml:mi></mml:mrow></mml:msub></mml:mrow></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="41598_2021_91513_Article_IEq21.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula>) , and (2) the count of high-synchrony peaks of the PST-histogram considering a threshold of <inline-formula id="IEq22"><alternatives><tex-math id="M43">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
