        <p id="Par24">Considering the three regimes on the whole, AEIF and LIFL are the models whose behavior is most similar, presumably reflecting the affinity of their neurocomputational profile. Specifically, in the SD example they present a similar value of <inline-formula id="IEq26"><alternatives><tex-math id="M51">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
