          <p id="Par49">For a given neuron <italic>j</italic> in active mode, the arrival of new input contributions implies <inline-formula id="IEq97"><alternatives><tex-math id="M207">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
